### `run` — single probe pass — IMPLEMENTED
1. Parse `<binary> --help` → extract commands & options (parser.py)
2. Run every subcommand --help, then every boolean flag (runner.py)
3. Local analysis of exit codes and failures (analyzer.py fallback_report)
4. Generate JSON report + terminal output → saved to runs/ (report.py, cli_tester.py)

### `evolve` — self-improving loop — IMPLEMENTED
- Timestamped run directories with conversation logs and probe results
- Each round runs as separate subprocess (evolve.py)
- One improvement per round cycle (system prompt enforces this)
- Git commit + push after each round with conventional commit format
- Re-probe after fixes with cache clearing
- CONVERGED marker detection

